Value: Adore Beauty Group Limited operates an integrated content, marketing, and e-commerce retail platform in Australia and New Zealand. The company primarily retails beauty and personal care products, including skincare, make-up, haircare, fragrance, and wellness products under various brands. It also offers editorial content on beauty news, reviews, tips, and expert how-to articles to educate the customers on purchasing decisions. The company was founded in 2000 and is headquartered in Northcote, Australia.
